We are given like an hour break after deciding on how the final games would work.  So Bastian and I head up to our room to chill for a bit and Martin comes in.  We talk then decide it&#146;s time to head down.  Martin, Bastian, and Hunter all choose to play light against their opponents: Brad, Shannon, and Andy, respectively.  I opt to play dark, as I did earlier, against Scott.<br>
